[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;75r\u001b[72;1H; regenerates the session ID if the browser sends an uninitialized session ID.\u001b[72;33H"]
[0.033, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;73r\u001b8\r\u001b[73d"]
[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;75r\u001b[72;1H; Strict mode protects applications from session fixation via a session adoption\u001b[72;33H"]
[0.033, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;73r\u001b8\r\u001b[73d"]
[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;75r\u001b[72;1H; vulnerability. It is disabled by default for maximum compatibility, but\u001b[72;33H"]
[0.033, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;73r\u001b8\r\u001b[73d"]
[0.001, "o", "\n\u001b[1;75r\u001b[72;1H; enabling it is encouraged."]
